# License

This repository is released under **mixed licenses**. Most content is licensed
under CC BY 4.0, but content derived from the Hungarian Universal Dependencies
treebank (UD_Hungarian-Szeged) is licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 to match its
source license. See the breakdown below for exactly what falls under each term.

---

## CC BY 4.0 — Attribution 4.0 International (default license)

Unless explicitly listed under CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 below, all content in this
repository — including all code, scripts, the Azerbaijani/Turkish/Finnish
derived datasets, the Turkic combined dataset (AZ+TR), the out-of-domain
Wikipedia annotations, evaluation results, figures, and trained-model outputs —
is released under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International license.

Full license text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/legalcode

This means you are free to share, adapt, and use this content for any purpose,
including commercially, provided you give appropriate credit. See "Citation"
below for how to attribute.

---

## CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 — Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 3.0 (Hungarian-derived content)

The following files are derived from UD_Hungarian-Szeged, which is licensed
under CC BY-NC-SA 3.0. As required by that license's ShareAlike term, all
derivative content is released under the same license:

- `data/morph_hun.tsv`
- `data/train_hun.tsv`
- `data/val_hun.tsv`
- `data/test_hun.tsv`
- `data/morph_uralic.tsv` (contains Hungarian-derived rows)
- `data/train_uralic.tsv` (contains Hungarian-derived rows)
- `data/train_all4.tsv` (contains Hungarian-derived rows)
- `data/ud-treebanks/UD_Hungarian-Szeged/*.conllu` (original treebank files,
  redistributed here under their original license)

Full license text: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/legalcode

**This means the files above may not be used for commercial purposes, and any
derivative works built from them must also be released under CC BY-NC-SA 3.0.**
This restriction does not apply to any other file in this repository.

