## Third-party sources

This repository redistributes or derives from the following third-party
resources. Their original licenses govern the underlying material independent
of the terms above:

| Source | License | Used for |
|---|---|---|
| UniMorph 4.0 (Batsuren et al., 2022) | CC BY-SA 3.0 | Inflection tables (all 4 languages) |
| UD_Azerbaijani-TueCL | CC BY-SA 4.0 | Azerbaijani treebank data |
| UD_Turkish-BOUN | CC BY-SA 4.0 | Turkish treebank data |
| UD_Turkish-IMST | CC BY-SA 4.0 | Turkish treebank data |
| UD_Finnish-TDT | CC BY-SA 4.0 | Finnish treebank data |
| UD_Hungarian-Szeged | CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 | Hungarian treebank data (see above) |
| Wikipedia (aze/tur/hun/fin editions) | CC BY-SA | Source words for out-of-domain evaluation (words used, not redistributed as Wikipedia text) |

Per-treebank `LICENSE.txt` files are included alongside each treebank under
`data/ud-treebanks/`.

